THE WOLF
	: girl, wolf
- girl passes by town buildings, and notices boxes in front of one building
- boxes contain dogs/wolves, who are all frozen
	- sign on boxes says "free puppy donations?"
	- one younger wolf still alive 
- mother comes up and says wolves are all dead/frozen 
- girl collects one living wolf and group continues toward warehouse/BOT building down the town street

THE CLIMB 
	: mother 
- group runs through town, and finds building warehouse, open area
- in open area is giant "bot", with large magnet arm 
- mother makes treacherous climb through building, onto robot ladder
	near death falls (toward main control chassis of giant BOT)
	- mother climbs up ladder, and holds on to unstable bar
	- bar slips in and out of place between two ends 
	- mother inserts bar into place at right end, and makes leap, holding bar, to next bar above
	- mother barely catches upper bar, and unstable bar falls down to ground far below
	- mother makes more leaps toward control chassis

THE "odor" BOMB 
	: mother
- in control area, mother uses giant BOT magnet arm to grab "odor" bomb
- shoots "odor" bomb at "Money Building"
	- "Money Building" explosion
	- warehouse building around BOT begins to collapse
	- mother slides down from BOT down to building below, where girl and boy companion (younger) are
	
A FLEE 
	: mother, girl boy companion (younger)
- group begins to flee collapsing building (building resembles a "tiered parking lot structure")
